EPIC:

        Press the 'LEFT SHIFT' and slowly type "NEM YDID EHT" and press
        'RETURN'.  You'll hear a sound.  Now 'C' will complete your
        mission.

        Push the joystick down and to the right and press 'ENTER' for full
        shields and weapons.

                                 (LEVEL CODES)

        1-"AURIGA"  2-"CEPHEUS"  3-"APUS"  4-"MUSCA"  5-"PYXIS"  6-"CETUS"
                        7-"FORNAX"  8-"CAELUM"  9-"CORVUS"
